<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>실습. POST로 정보 받기</title>
        <style>
            .color {
                display: inline-block;
                width: 40px;
                height: 20px;
                vertical-align: top;
                background-color: <%= userInfo.favoriteColor %>;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h2>회원 가입이 완료되었습니다!</h2>
        <h3>회원 정보</h3>
        <div>이름 : <%= userInfo.name %></div>
        <div>성별 : <%- userInfo.gender === 'male' ? '남자' : '여자' %></div>
        <div>생년월일 : <%= userInfo.birthYear %>-<%= userInfo.birthMonth %>-<%= userInfo.birthDate %></div>
        <br />
        <hr />
        <div>취미 : <%- userInfo.hobby ? userInfo.hobby : '없음' %></div>
        <div>좋아하는 색상 <span class="color"></span></div>
        <div>
            좋아하는 숫자 :
            <span><%- userInfo.favoriteNumber ? userInfo.favoriteNumber : "없음" %> </span>
        </div>
        <div>
            메일 주소 : <span><span><%- userInfo.myEmail ? userInfo.myEmail : "미입력" %> </span></span>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
